Version:        2.28
Release:        3%{?dist}
Summary:        Interface to Bzip2 compression library
# bzlib-src/win-tst-dlltest.c (unbundled):  Public Domain
# bzlib-src/LICENSE (unbundled):            BSD
# bzlib-src/manual.ps (unbundled):          GPL+ with exception
